the disney vacation club (dvc) offers ownership interests in seven resort facilities located at the walt
disney world resort; vero beach, florida; and hilton head island, south carolina. available units at each facility are offered for sale under a vacation ownership plan and are operated as rental property until the units are sold. disneys
