eitf d-108  in september
2004, the emerging issues task force (eitf) issued topic no. d-108, use of the residual method to value acquired assets other than goodwill (eitf d-108). eitf d-108 requires that a direct value method be used to value intangible assets
acquired in business combinations completed after september29, 2004. eitf d-108 also requires the company to perform an impairment test using a direct value method on all intangible assets that were previously valued using the residual method.
